---
title: Ranch and Tortilla Crunch Burgers with Seasoned Potato Wedges and Cheddar
description: Get ready for a flavour explosion with our Ranch and Tortilla Crunch Burger! These juicy patties are smothered in melted cheese, topped with a zesty ranch and toasted tortilla crunch and served with perfectly seasoned potato wedges. It's a fun and delicious combo that will have your tastebuds begging for more!

