ic acid, canola oil, oleoresin paprika, silicon dioxide) (sulphites) • Zesty garlic blend (granulated garlic, cornmeal, salt, dehydrated red bell pepper flakes, spices, sugar, herbs, canola oil, silicon dioxide, citric acid) (sulphites).
